<heading>session current - Show current session.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  session current
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Displays the active session key and its client, home,
and flow counts.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
list, attach, detach, man
</paragraph>
